Ocean Power Collaborates With Lockheed Martin on Wave Energy

-- B y   L o u i s e   D o w n i n g
-- 
2011-09-13T11:14:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-13/ocean-power-collaborates-with-lockheed-martin-on-wave-energy.html
Ocean Power Technologies Inc. (OPTT)  said
it agreed to collaborate with  Lockheed Martin Corp. (LMT)  on a
commercial-scale wave power generation project
at Reedsport, Oregon.  The venture follows a $2.4 million contract awarded to
Ocean Power from the U.S. Department of Energy, according to a
statement on Business Wire today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Louise Downing in London at 
 ldowning4@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Reed Landberg at 
 landberg@bloomberg.net  